OL,3,CMP accused of misusing campaign funds
OL,4,Cresigns from Tory Party
OL,6,FFylde MP Mark Menzies has resigned
OL,7,Ffrom the Conservative Party and will
OL,8,Fleave Parliament at the next election.
OL,9,FIt comes after police said they were
OL,10,F'reviewing' a letter in relation to
OL,11,Fallegations against the MP, who was
OL,12,Faccused of misusing campaign funds.
OL,14,FThe Fylde MP has been accused of
OL,15,Fmisusing political donations to cover
OL,16,Fhis medical expenses and pay off "bad
OL,17,Fpeople" who had locked him in a flat
OL,18,Fand demanded money for his release.
