OL,6,FAn investigation into the allegations,
OL,7,Fdenied by Mr Menzies, concluded on
OL,8,FSunday, finding that while there had
OL,9,Fnot been a misuse of party funds, the
OL,10,FMP's behaviour fell below the required
OL,11,Fstandards and may have breached the
OL,12,FNolan principles of public life.
OL,14,FThe backbench MP for Fylde in
OL,15,FLancashire disputed the allegations
OL,16,Fbut was suspended from the
OL,17,FConservative parliamentary party while
OL,18,Fan investigation took place.
