OL,6,FIn a statement, Mr Menzies said: "It
OL,7,Fhas been an enormous privilege
OL,8,Frepresenting the people of Fylde since
OL,9,F2010.
OL,11,F"Due to the pressures on myself and my
OL,12,Felderly mother, I have decided to
OL,13,Fresign from the Conservative Party and
OL,14,Fwill not stand at the forthcoming
OL,15,Fgeneral election."
OL,17,FLancashire Police said it was
OL,18,Freviewing "information" about Mr
OL,19,FMenzies after Labour asked for an
OL,20,Finvestigation.
