OL,4,Cresigns from Tory Party
OL,6,FThe Times reported that Mr Menzies had
OL,7,Fcalled his 78-year old former campaign
OL,8,Fmanager, Kate Fieldhouse, at 3.15am
OL,9,Fone day in December, claiming he was
OL,10,Flocked in a flat and needed #5,000 as
OL,11,Fa matter of "life and death".
OL,13,FThe sum, which rose to #6,500, was
OL,14,Feventually paid by his office manager
OL,15,Ffrom her personal bank account and
OL,16,Fsubsequently reimbursed from funds
OL,17,Fraised from donors in an account named
OL,18,FFylde Westminster Group, it is alleged.
