OL,6,FThe newspaper reported that #14,000
OL,7,Fgiven by donors for Tory campaign
OL,8,Factivities was transferred to Mr
OL,9,FMenzies' personal bank accounts and
OL,10,Fused for private medical expenses.
OL,12,FOn Sunday, a party spokesman said the
OL,13,Fmoney in question had been signed off
OL,14,Fby two signatories of the Fylde
OL,15,FWestminster Group.
