OL,6,FThey said: "This body sits outside of
OL,7,Fthe remit of both the Conservative
OL,8,FParty and Fylde Conservative
OL,9,FAssociation. Therefore we cannot
OL,10,Fconclude that there has been a misuse
OL,11,Fof Conservative Party funds.
OL,13,F"We do believe that there has been a
OL,14,Fpattern of behaviour that falls below
OL,15,Fthe standards expected of MPs and
OL,16,Findividuals looking after donations to
OL,17,Flocal campaign funds."
