OL,6,FOpposition parties have called for the
OL,7,Fpolice to investigate the allegations
OL,8,Fmade against Mr Menzies, and
OL,9,FLancashire Police said it was
OL,10,F"reviewing the available information"
OL,11,Fafter receiving a complaint,
OL,12,Funderstood to have been made by Labour
OL,13,FParty chairwoman Anneliese Dodds.
OL,15,FAnneliese Dodds has said Mark Menzies
OL,16,F"did the right thing" in deciding to
OL,17,Fleave Parliament, but "serious
OL,18,Fquestions remain for Rishi Sunak and
OL,19,Fthe Conservative Party".
