OL,6,FShe said: "The fact that Conservatives
OL,7,Fhave not even approached the
OL,8,Fwhistleblowers in the case, weeks
OL,9,Fafter saying they were going to,
OL,10,Fdespite now saying the investigation
OL,11,Fhas been completed, says everything
OL,12,Fabout how seriously they are dealing
OL,13,Fwith these allegations.
OL,15,F"The Conservative Chairman and Chief
OL,16,FWhip need to immediately come out of
OL,17,Fhiding and explain what action they
OL,18,Fhave taken to deal with these shocking
OL,19,Fallegations.
