OL,6,F"And Rishi Sunak needs to explain how
OL,7,Fhe will ever deliver on his promise of
OL,8,Fprofessionalism, integrity and
OL,9,Faccountability and drag his party out
OL,10,Fof the morass of constant sleaze."
OL,12,FThe Conservatives said they would
OL,13,F"share any information with the police
OL,14,Fif they believe it would be helpful to
OL,15,Fany investigation they decide to
OL,16,Fundertake".
OL,18,FMr Menzies has been MP for Fylde since
OL,19,F2010, and won a majority of 16,611 at
OL,20,Fthe last election.
